{"tid":1299616,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（理性討論＋法律撚請入）點解林鄭咁堅持唔撤回？同被控暴動義士有關？","createTime":"2019-07-09T06:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T10:13:20.000Z","uid":83487,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b97ac3f6a43760153f8a995a2904f445ce455d2d","tid":1299616,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"大家都知道撤回同暫緩最唔同既地方係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">撤回</span></span>係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">有法律效力</span></span>而暫緩係冇<br />\n <br />\n所以假設條例真係「撤回」<br />\n即係政府要徹底承認條例喺法律上完全失效<br />\n同時都可能要承擔埋因為硬推呢條條例而所帶嚟既法律責任<br />\n <br />\n參考暴動罪定義同埋下面篇文<br />\n <br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\">3人或多於3人集結在一起，意圖破壞社會安寧，就是有組織性的破壞行為，是暴動罪成立的基礎</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1064356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1064356&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1aRE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=b66e1f2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1064356&h=bde9afa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1064356</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">動機</span></span>與<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">意圖</span></span>在法律上關係是極為關連的，而非彭寶琴所誤導為各有各獨立的。先明白兩者的關係，陪審團方能準確判斷本案所需的暴動意圖是甚麼，而更重要的是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">有需要確定其存在</span></span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://wongonyin.mysinablog.com/index.php?op=ViewArticle&amp;articleId=20300789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwongonyin.mysinablog.com%2Findex.php%3Fop%3DViewArticle%26articleId%3D20300789&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1aRE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=5ed2ce98\" target=\"_blank\">http://wongonyin.mysinablog.com/index.php?op=ViewArticle&amp;articleId=20300789</a><br />\n <br />\n如果用返今次612被控暴動義士做例子<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">犯案動機: 阻止政府硬推送中條例<br />\n犯案意圖(警狗所講): 破壞社會安寧</span></span><br />\n <br />\n但如果政府「撤回」送中<br />\n咁即係法律上 犯案動機本身就唔應該存在<br />\n再推落去 <span style=\"color: gold;\">犯罪意圖</span>本身都應該<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔存在</span><br />\n冇意圖　就唔會犯暴動罪<br />\n <br />\n小弟冇讀過法律<br />\n純粹自己同朋友傾開點解林鄭咁堅持唔撤回<br />\n再諗到既其中一個可能性<br />\n希望大家　特別係法律JJ 可以一齊討論下！"},{"pid":"ffb08b7d9c7a02de4698154149b85a20f4bf1f59","tid":1299616,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0df934c19f322a5a51d33545f8eac250aef0159","tid":1299616,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec208a959a93a59a260a95d09b2902b041643df","tid":1299616,"uid":259928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:05:18.000Z","msg":"多一個視角俾大家知道點解林鄭唔肯撤，分析政府官員邏輯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299053</a>"},{"pid":"410b9a9f37d33b27e41c70256d1947bb078b3c47","tid":1299616,"uid":83487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fec208a959a93a59a260a95d09b2902b041643df","tid":1299616,"uid":259928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:05:18.000Z","msg":"多一個視角俾大家知道點解林鄭唔肯撤，分析政府官員邏輯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299053</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"巴打英雄所見略同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811fa2e587cec7aa8d4ec5f0fb5f5daf4f65e896","tid":1299616,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,